reviewText: Episodes:  My Dad The Smuggler, I Am Not a Terrorist, Hasidic King of Coke, Not Without My Baby, Chilean Prison Break, The Orchid Hunters, Venezuela Hustle, Nightmare in Somalia, Busted in Bangkok, and Escape from the Gulag.

VERY PROMPT DELIVERY TIME AND WELL PACKAGED.  IT WAS FOE A XMAS GIFT AND IT ARRIVED JUST IN TIME.  THE STORIES ARE EXCELLENT AND A MUST FOR ANYONE WHO IS CONSIDERING OF TRAVELING OUT OF THE USA.  WELL WORTH THE MONEY AND TIME WATCHING!!!
